#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.core.__lshift__"
msgstr "# triton.language.core.__lshift__"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:4
msgid "简介：根据给定值 将tensor张量进行左移位。"
msgstr "Introduction: Perform a left shift on the tensor according to the given value."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.core.__lshift__(\n"
" input: tl.tensor,\n"
" other: tl.tensor,\n"
" builder: ir.builder\n"
") -> tl.tensor\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:8
msgid "作为`tensor`的内置运算符使用，如`x<<y`。"
msgstr "Used as a built-in operator for `tensor`, such as `x<<y`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:10
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:12
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:14
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | --- |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | 张量数据，左操作数，代表要进行移位的主数据 |\n"
"| `other`   | `tensor or scalar` | 张量数据，右操作数，进行移位的数值 |\n"
"| `_builder` | - | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Description |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | --- |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | Tensor data, left operand, representing the main data to be shifted |\n"
"| `other` | `tensor or scalar` | Tensor data, right operand, the value by which to shift |\n"
"| `_builder` | - | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:16
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tl.tensor`：同`input`的shape的张量\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tl.tensor`: a tensor with the same shape as `input`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:18
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:20
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:22
msgid ""
"|       | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n"
"| GPU      | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | × | × | × | × | √ |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √ | √ | √ | × | × | × | × | √ | × | × | × | × | √ |\n"
msgstr ""
"|       | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n"
"| GPU      | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | × | × | × | × | √ |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √ | √ | √ | × | × | × | × | √ | × | × | × | × | √ |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:24
msgid "结论：Ascend 对比 GPU 缺失uint的支持能力。"
msgstr "Conclusion: Ascend lacks support for uint compared to GPU."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:26
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:28
msgid ""
"|        | 支持维度范围         |\n"
"| -------- | ---------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | 无限制 |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | 无限制 |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | Supported Dimension Range |\n"
"| -------- | ---------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | Unlimited |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | Unlimited |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:30
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异。"
msgstr "Conclusion: There is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms in terms of Shape."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:32
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Limitations"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:34
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability deficiency and inability to achieve"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:36
msgid ""
"1. Ascend 相比 GPU 缺失 uint 类型支持。\n"
"2. 右操作数 `other` 仅支持标量，不支持 tensor（即 `x << 2` 合法，`x << y`（`y` 为 tensor）暂不支持）。\n"
msgstr ""
"1. Ascend lacks support for the `uint` type compared to GPU.  \n"
"2. The right operand `other` only supports scalars, not tensors (i.e., `x << 2` is valid, while `x << y` (where `y` is a tensor) is not yet supported).\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:38
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:40
msgid "以下示例实现了对三维张量`x0`、`x1`做左移位运算："
msgstr "The following example implements left shift operation on three-dimensional tensors `x0` and `x1`:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/lshift.md:42
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def triton_lshift_3d(in_ptr0, out_ptr0, L : tl.constexpr, M : tl.constexpr, N : tl.constexpr):\n"
"    loffs = tl.program_id(0) * L\n"
"    lblk_idx = tl.arange(0,L) + loffs\n"
"    mblk_idx = tl.arange(0,M)\n"
"    nblk_idx = tl.arange(0,N)\n"
"    idx = lblk_idx[:,None,None]*N*M+mblk_idx[None,:,None]*N+nblk_idx[None,None,:]\n"
"    x0=tl.load(in_ptr0+idx)\n"
"    ret = x0 << 2\n"
"    odx = lblk_idx[:, None, None] * N * M + mblk_idx[None, :, None] * N + nblk_idx[None, None, :]\n"
"    tl.store(out_ptr0+odx, ret)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

